<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10726511>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Chartergus metanotalis Richards, 1978—A: lateral view. B: dorsal view. C: face, frontal view. D: nest. Paratype of Chartergus metanotalis—E: lateral. F: dorsal. G: original label." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10726511/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10726513>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Map showing the current geographicdistribution of Chartergus species.For locality information see Supplementary material S1." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10726513/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10726515>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Phylogenetic relationships of Chartergus species inferred by Maximum Likelihood (A) and Maximum Parsimony (B) analysis using COI mitochondrial and morphological data. Values at the nodes represent Shimodaira-Hasegawa approximate likelihood ratio test/parametric ultrafast bootstrap (left) and symmetric resampling (right) supports as reported by IQ-Tree (A) and TNT (B), respectively." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10726515/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

